01:01:36.056 --> 01:01:38.250
want to lose you.
 

01:01:38.250 --> 01:01:41.059
I know there is only one class
but I don't want to lose you.

01:01:41.059 --> 01:01:44.268
Of course the only--the way in
which Dante's conveying all

01:01:44.268 --> 01:01:47.139
these senses is by playing with
the etymologies,

01:01:47.139 --> 01:01:51.170
because etymology is the
science of the origin of words,

01:01:51.170 --> 01:01:53.329
so let me give you only one.
 

